PROBLEM 5:

Configure your .bashrc and .bash_profile file both

    1.configure your history output so that it can give date and time of command along with command name example:- date 12 june 2020 9:30 AM
    2.Max history size for all users will be 5000
    3.for root user history must be stored under /opt/roothist.txt
    4.make sure root user can run chmod command
    5.set your terminal prompt like this : "DelVex@root:- "
    
SOLUTION:
2. HISTSIZE=5000
#write inside .bashrc file to make it  persistent
5.PS1="DelVex@root:- "
